Hello,




We hope you're enjoying ordering and delivery with MenuStar.



*We want to inform you that the Ordering Fee will soon change to 16%
beginning on October 1st, 2022.*





*The Ordering Fee is paid by the customers when placing an order.  This
means you will continue to enjoy free no commission ordering.  There is no
fee for the restaurant.*





Your MenuStar account will continue to include these features for free:

=E2=80=A2            Unlimited orders and no commission per order.

=E2=80=A2            Restaurant branded website (including hosting).

=E2=80=A2            Internet Marketing using Search Engine Optimization (S=
EO) so
that customers can find your restaurant.

=E2=80=A2            Delivery services.

=E2=80=A2            Live ordering alert, notification, confirmation.

=E2=80=A2            And much more.





At MenuStar, we understand that business today looks nothing like it did
yesterday. Our work never stops in connecting you with new customers using
new technology.



*Should you have any questions please don=E2=80=99t hesitate to contact our
Customer Support Team at **support@themenustar.com*
<support@themenustar.com>*. We appreciate your business and thank you for
choosing MenuStar. *





Sincerely,

The MenuStar Team

