Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit

 

 

Hello,


 

We hope you're enjoying ordering and delivery with MenuStar. 

 

We want to inform you that the Ordering Fee will soon change to 16%
beginning on October 1st, 2022.

 

 

The Ordering Fee is paid by the customers when placing an order.  This means
you will continue to enjoy free no commission ordering.  There is no fee for
the restaurant.

 

 

Your MenuStar account will continue to include these features for free:

.            Unlimited orders and no commission per order.

.            Restaurant branded website (including hosting).

.            Internet Marketing using Search Engine Optimization (SEO) so
that customers can find your restaurant.

.            Delivery services.

.            Live ordering alert, notification, confirmation.

.            And much more.

 

 

At MenuStar, we understand that business today looks nothing like it did
yesterday. Our work never stops in connecting you with new customers using
new technology.

 

Should you have any questions please don't hesitate to contact our Customer
Support Team at  <mailto:support@themenustar.com> support@themenustar.com.
We appreciate your business and thank you for choosing MenuStar. 

 

 

Sincerely,

The MenuStar Team


